JAPAN: Japan offers 1.0 trln yen 3.1 pct 10-year bond.Japan offers 1.0 trln yen 3.1 pct 10-year bond.The Ministry of Finance said on Wednesday that it was offering 1.0 trillion yen worth of 3.1 percent 10-year Japanese government bonds (JGBs) through a price-competitive auction.The auction will close at noon (0300 GMT) and the results will be announced at 2.30 p.m. (0530 GMT).The issue date is September 20, and maturity date is September 20, 2006.